Class AbstractEventHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • burtis.common.events.AbstractEventHandler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BusScheduler, PassengerModuleEventHandler, Server, SimulationEventHandler, SyncEventHandler

    public abstract class AbstractEventHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides default processing abilities for all events. Inheriting classes should override process method for interesting events.
    Author:
    Amadeusz Sadowski
